research_municipality_step.notes: Crowley, TX operates under a Council-Manager government. The Mayor and City Council members are listed based on the city's staff directory. Some sources indicate that the terms for Mayor Billy Davis (May 2025), Jerry Beck Jr. (May 2025), Jesse D. Johnson (May 2025), Jim Hirth (May 2024), and Scott Gilbreath (May 2023) may have expired. However, they are still listed as current officials on the city's official staff directory.
